EnExplanation: A pronoun used in the context of referring to a group of people or things previously mentioned, indicating a relationship or possession.

Samples.EeSentence: Need raamatud on neist kõige huvitavamad.
Samples.EnSentence: These books are the most interesting of them.

Samples.EeSentence: Need on mu sõbrad ja neist ma hoolin.
Samples.EnSentence: These are my friends and I care about them.
